                        <interp inst="t18450707-1472-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 17.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor and Jury.—
<rs id="t18450707-1472-punishment-17" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18450707-1472-punishment-17" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
